# Input file for `scriptmaker` (if desired)
program name                dms
program version             1.02
program oneliner            oneliner description
program description         longer description
program arg_type            [ options ]
program style               default

parent name               
parent version            
parent release_date       

author name                 Your Name Here
author email                you at domain.org
author homepage             http://www.domain.org/

do_preamble                 0
do_config_file              1
do_docs                     1
do_options                  1
do_debug                    1
do_comments                 1

related foobar              http://www.foobar.org

feature file_ops            Useful file system routines
feature templates           Template toolkit support
#feature database            Database (DBI) support
#feature logfile             Logfile parsing support
#feature xml                 XML parsing support
#feature gd                  GD support
#feature test                Regression test
#feature lwp                 Web robot functionality
#feature filter              Text filter support
#feature svg                 SVG generation/parsing support
#feature mod_perl            mod_perl/Apache support
#feature cgi                 CGI application support
#feature validation          Text input data validation
#feature datafile            Datafile parsing/formatting support

option boolean version|V     Prints the version and exits
option boolean help|h        Prints a brief help message
option boolean helplong|H    Prints a long help message
option boolean man           Prints a manual page (detailed help)
option integer debug|D       Prints debug messages



